 rвҶҗTest_InstallAndLoad_095(stopFlag batchFlag);вҺ•TRAP;targetDir;res;rc;msg;targetDir2
вҚқ Install and load a package from the local test server as usual and then in MyApp._tatin
 вҺ•TRAPвҶҗ(999 'C' '. вҚқ Deliberate error')(0 'N')
 rвҶҗT._Failed

 #.вҺ•EX TC.GetTatinRootSpace'#'
 #.вҺ•SHADOW'TEMP' вӢ„ 'TEMP'#.вҺ•NS'' вҚқ Used to load stuff into
 targetDirвҶҗвҲҶGetTempDir''
 resвҶҗTC.InstallPackages'[localhost]example-versions-1.0.12-zzz'targetDir
 вҶ’T.GoToTidyUp'example-versions-1.0.12-zzz'вүўвҲҠres
 resвҶҗTC.LoadDependencies targetDir #.TEMP
 вҶ’T.GoToTidyUp'#._tatin.example_versions_1_0_12_zzz'вүў' '~вҚЁвҚ•res
 вҶ’T.GoToTidyUp'MyCode'вүўвҠғ#.TEMP.versions.Version
 вҶ’T.GoToTidyUp 1вү вүў#._tatin.вҺ•NLвҚі16

 #.вҺ•SHADOW'MyApp' вӢ„ 'MyApp'#.вҺ•NS''
 targetDir2вҶҗвҲҶGetTempDir''
 resвҶҗTC.InstallPackages'[localhost]example-versions-1'targetDir2
 вҶ’T.GoToTidyUp'example-versions-1.0.12-That-fix'вүўвҲҠres
 resвҶҗTC.LoadDependencies targetDir2 #.MyApp #.MyApp
 вҶ’T.GoToTidyUp 0=#.MyApp.вҺ•NC'_tatin'
 вҶ’T.GoToTidyUp 0=#.MyApp._tatin.вҺ•NC'example-versions-1.0.12-That-fix'
 вҶ’T.GoToTidyUp'MyCode'вүўвҠғ#.MyApp._tatin.example_versions_1_0_12_That_fix.MyCode.Version
 вҶ’T.GoToTidyUp 1вү вүў#.MyApp._tatin.вҺ•NLвҚі16
 вҶ’T.GoToTidyUp 1вү вүў#._tatin.вҺ•NLвҚі16
 вҶ’T.GoToTidyUp'MyCode'вүўвҠғ#.MyApp.versions.Version

 rвҶҗT._OK

вҲҶTidyUp:
 (rc msg)вҶҗF.RmDirByForce targetDir
 msg Assert rc=0
 (rc msg)вҶҗF.RmDirByForce targetDir2
 msg Assert rc=0
 #.вҺ•EX TC.GetTatinRootSpace'#'
вҚқDone
